----------------------
Showing toast message 
----------------------
step 1: 
import the Package: npm i ngx-toastr --save
 
step 2:
angular.json (file) : Styles>> add>> "node_modules/ngx-toastr/toastr.css"


Import the following in app.module.ts


>>import{BrowserAnimationsModule} from '@angular/platform-browser/animations'
>>import { ToastrModule } from 'ngx-toastr';

@import[
  ToastrModule.forRoot(),// for global call
  BrowserAnimationsModule,
]
>>Import the toaster for the particaular page
import { ToastrService } from 'ngx-toastr';
constructor >> Add>>  private ToastrService: ToastrService

ex: this.ToastrService.success('message')

  
To Use Toast Message
---------------------
  
  show toast               show
  show successful toast >> success 
  show error toast      >> error
  show info toast       >> info
  show warning toast    >> warning
   